# vtest - a minimal unit test framework

## Instructions
See include/vtest.h for API and vtest_example.c for an example.

    $ cc -Iinclude -std=c99 -Wall -Wextra -pedantic vtest_example.c vtest.c -o vtest_example
    $ ./vtest_example 
    
    -----------------
    PASS: 2
    FAIL: 2
     main:7 '0 == 1'
     main:10 '!"I should fail"'
    -----------------
    $ 

